Detailed Description

HDF5 database backup file implementation.

Provides read/write access to an HDF5 database backup file.

When creating a backup file, the version of this software must match the server version. When reading a backup file, the versions may be different.

The HDF5 file has the following layout:

  • /enums/<enumname>/ contains enumeration definitions
  • /objects/<classname>/ contains class objects
  • /arrays/<classname>/id<id>/data contains array data
  • /arrays/<classname>/id<id>/<axis>Axis contains array axis definition
  • /signals/<classname>/id<id>/data contains signal data
  • /signals/<classname>/id<id>/<axis>Axis contains signal axis definition
